      "FacilityID": 48216,
      "SummaryText": "documented for each location) to land in the event of an emergency response. \n\nThe NTMWD has held training classes on-site with the Wylie Fire Department, and other local industry representative. The classes included the Wylie Fire Marshall, Wylie ERT, Wylie EMTs, and Wylie Firemen. The classes were designed to allow each industry and the fire department to become more familiar with the facility and as a community understands the resources each have in the event of an emergency.\n\nThe NTMWD believes that the success to an emergency response situation is proper planning and working with local responders. Our goal is continue the excellent relationship that we have with the Wylie Fire Department and provide reliable services to the citizens served by the District."
